{
  "stem": "22447.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's when it started, the day after, because they knew if that invasion failed, they can't launch another one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Had they come in June 1940, they could have just walked into England, but then it-- they couldn't do anything else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then after that, I-- we went-- after six months, we went back to the mainland and Newbury Racecourse.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, just training, what they used to say, training, more to give us a rest because we was there six weeks, six months.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was six months on the coast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very boring, very monotonous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just-- that's why I've never gone back to the Isle of Wight.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just stood down the-- on the beaches and waited for an invasion to happen, which is not a pleasant thing and nothing's happening.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the night, it gets very cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the day time, it's very hot and the night time gets very cold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Afterwards they said we can go into Ventnor once a week for a few hours, but the army, they have their own shows, you know, the army shows.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to make their own entertainment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] wasn't started up yet in 1940.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was no-- nothing really for you to do at all--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very boring.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You was just-- you didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This went on till December.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "December we went to the, shifted to Newbury, onto the race course.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was bitterly cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Christmas, 1940, it was very cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the water froze up and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, I got posted back to-- no, I was in-- I had some problem with my leg and there was a regulation, if you were away from your unit 21 days, you got sent back to your depot.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I knew about this regulation.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
